stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle --> Loading : selectStory()
    Loading --> Buffering : streamStarted
    Loading --> Error : fetchFailed

    Buffering --> Playing : bufferReady
    Buffering --> Error : streamError

    Playing --> Paused : pause()
    Playing --> Buffering : bufferUnderrun
    Playing --> Completed : reachedEnd
    Playing --> Error : playbackError

    Paused --> Playing : resume()
    Paused --> Idle : stop()
    Paused --> Loading : selectStory()

    Completed --> Idle : dismiss()
    Completed --> Loading : replay()
    Completed --> Loading : selectStory()

    Error --> Loading : retry()
    Error --> Idle : dismiss()

    note right of Loading
        RACE CONDITION ZONE
        User taps new story while
        previous story is still loading.
        Old callback fires after context
        switch causing wrong audio playback.
        FIX: AudioPlayerContext serializes
        all transitions with generation ID.
        Stale callbacks are rejected.
    end note

    note right of Buffering
        Buffer callbacks carry a
        storyId. Context rejects
        callbacks where storyId
        does not match current.
    end note
